<div class="post">
  <ul class="mt-2 ml-0 grid list-none grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4">
    {% for link in links %}
      <li class="mb-2 pl-2">
        <a
          href="{{ link.url }}"
          target="_blank"
        >
          {{- link.title -}}
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  <hr class="my-5">
  <div class="pl-2">
    <a href="https://webring.xxiivv.com/" class="block w-[128px]"
      ><img src="https://webring.xxiivv.com/icon.white.svg"
    ></a>
    <p>
      This <a href="https://webring.xxiivv.com">webring</a> is an attempt to inspire artists &amp; developers to build
      their own website and share traffic among each other. The ring welcomes personalized websites such as diaries,
      wikis &amp; portfolios.
    </p>
    <p>
      To add yourself to the ring, submit a
      <a href="https://github.com/XXIIVV/webring#join-the-webring">pull request</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
